*   [CSVKit](https://csvkit.readthedocs.io/) - CSV utilities that includes csvsql / csvgrep / csvstat and more.

items.title: Awesome Json
items.content_text:
### Command-line tools

*   [jq (‚≠ê32k)](https://github.com/jqlang/jq) - A lightweight and flexible command-line JSON processor.
    *   [jaq (‚≠ê3.2k)](https://github.com/01mf02/jaq) - A jq clone focussed on correctness, speed, and simplicity. Written in Rust.
    *   [gojq (‚≠ê3.5k)](https://github.com/itchyny/gojq) - Pure Go implementation of jq. A bit faster and more portable.
